entry.title: WIND WARNING IN EFFECT, Dempster (Highway)
entry.summary: Persons in or near this area should be on the lookout for adverse weather conditions and take necessary safety precautions. Issued: 10:54 AM PDT Monday 16 May 2016

entry.title: Monday: Chance of flurries. Temperature steady near minus 4. POP 30%
entry.summary: Cloudy with 30 percent chance of flurries. Flurries over southern sections this afternoon. Local blowing snow near the Richardson mountains. Amount 4 cm over southern sections. Wind east 20 km/h except gusting to 70 near the Richardson mountains. Temperature steady near minus 4. Forecast issued 11:00 AM PDT Monday 16 May 2016
